{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"攒楛木的果实，"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"确是罪人的食品，"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"像油脚样在他们的腹中沸腾，"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"像开水一样地沸腾。"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"（主说）：“你们捉住他，然后，把他拖入火狱中，"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"然后，再把沸水的刑罚倾注在他的头上！ ”"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"你尝试吧！你确是显赫的，确是尊贵的！"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"这（刑罚）确是你们生前所怀疑的。”"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":51,"Text":"敬畏者必定要住在安全的地方"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"这里有园圃和源泉，"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":53,"Text":"穿着绫罗绸缎，相向而坐。"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":54,"Text":"结局是这样的：我将以白皙的、美目的女子，做他们的伴侣。"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":55,"Text":"他们在乐园中，将安全地索取各种水果。"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":56,"Text":"他们在乐园中，除初次死亡外不再尝死的滋味。安拉将使他们得免于火狱的刑罚。"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":57,"Text":"那是由于你的主的恩典，那确是伟大的成功。"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":58,"Text":"我以你的语言，使《古兰经》成为易解的，只为希望他们能觉悟。"},{"SurahNumber":44,"VerseNumber":59,"Text":"你等着吧，他们确是等待着的！"}]}